OL,3,CWhy have IT outages affected
OL,4,CMcDonald's, Tesco, Sainsbury's and
OL,5,CGreggs?
OL,7,FJames Bore is the managing director of
OL,8,FBores Group, a chartered technology
OL,9,Fand security company.
OL,11,FHe told ITV News that the "most
OL,12,Flikely" explanation for the IT outages
OL,13,Fwas an issue occurring during a live
OL,14,Fsystem update.
OL,16,F"This is the consequence of companies
OL,17,Fdeveloping massive, monolithic,
OL,18,Fincredibly complex systems, not
OL,19,Fmanaging their dependencies and not
OL,20,Fhaving proper quality testing before
OL,21,Fdeploying live," Mr Bore said.
