OL,3,CWhy have IT outages affected
OL,4,CMcDonald's, Tesco, Sainsbury's and
OL,5,CGreggs?
OL,7,FAsked how often technology updates are
OL,8,Fissued, Mr Bore explained it varies,
OL,9,Fwith most companies using a software
OL,10,Fdevelopment method called Agile, which
OL,11,Fuses 'Sprints' - a time-boxed period
OL,12,Fduring which work is carried out to
OL,13,Fcomplete a system update.
OL,15,FMr Bore said: "There's always faults
OL,16,Fand, again, the bigger the system, the
OL,17,Fmore complex it is, the more updates
OL,18,Fyou're going to get because they'll be
OL,19,Fto update just tiny fractions of that
OL,20,Fsystem."
